  "Description": {
    "English": "Specialist <span class=\"name name-technology\">Discovery</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Survey</span> unit.<br><br>Augments standard <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scanner</span> capabilities by projecting detailed environmental data directly over the user's visor. Allows the identification of <span class=\"name name-stellar\">distant points of interest</span>.<br><br>The Visor will generate <span class=\"name name-commodity\">valuable data</span> when used to study <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">flora</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">fauna</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">minerals</span>.<br><br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span> to operate. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">ZOOM</span> to zoom.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">探索</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">调查</span>的专业型装置。<br><br>通过将详细的环境数据直接投射至使用者的视觉系统来增强标准<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>的功能。可以识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">遥远的重要地点</span>。<br><br>面甲可在研究<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物群系</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">动物群系</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">矿物</span>时生成<span class=\"name name-commodity\">有价值的数据</span>。<br><br>按住<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>操作。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">ZOOM</span>缩放。",
    "TencentChinese": "用于<span class=\"name name-technology\">探索</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">调查</span>的专业型装置。<br><br>通过将详细的环境数据直接投射至使用者的视觉系统来增强标准<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>的功能。可以识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">遥远的兴趣点</span>。<br><br>面甲可在研究<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物群系</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">动物群系</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">矿物</span>时生成<span class=\"name name-commodity\">有价值的数据</span>。<br><br>按住<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>操作。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">ZOOM</span>缩放。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "專家<span class=\"name name-technology\">發現</span>與<span class=\"name name-technology\">調查</span>單元。<br><br>能強化標準的<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描器</span>，將詳細的環境資料直接投影至使用者的護目鏡。允許辨識<span class=\"name name-stellar\">遙遠的重要地點</span>。<br><br>使用護目鏡研究<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">動物</span>及<span class=\"name name-technology\">礦物</span>時，會產出<span class=\"name name-commodity\">珍貴資料</span>。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span> 操作。按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">ZOOM</span> 縮放。"
  },
