  "DamagedDescription": {
    "English": "The Analysis Visor is a planetary <span class=\"name name-technology\">exploration device</span> that locates and <span class=\"name name-technology\">highlights nearby points of interest</span>.<br><br>It can also be used to analyze <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">flora</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">fauna</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">minerals</span>. Analysis results in <span class=\"name name-commodity\">commercially valuable data</span>, as well as revealing <span class=\"name name-technology\">additional resources</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "分析面甲是一种星际<span class=\"name name-technology\">探索设备</span>，可以定位并<span class=\"name name-technology\">标记附近的兴趣点</span>。<br><br>也可以用于分析<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">动物</span>以及<span class=\"name name-technology\">矿物</span>。分析结果将得出<span class=\"name name-commodity\">商用宝贵数据</span>，并发现<span class=\"name name-technology\">额外资源</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "分析面甲是一种星际<span class=\"name name-technology\">探索设备</span>，可以定位并<span class=\"name name-technology\">标记附近的兴趣点</span>。<br><br>也可以用于分析<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">动物</span>以及<span class=\"name name-technology\">矿物</span>。分析结果将得出<span class=\"name name-commodity\">商用宝贵数据</span>，并发现<span class=\"name name-technology\">额外资源</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "分析護目鏡是行星<span class=\"name name-technology\">探索裝置</span>，能用來定位及<span class=\"name name-technology\">標示附近的重要地點</span>。<br><br>這種裝置也可以用來分析<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">動物</span>以及<span class=\"name name-technology\">礦物</span>。分析能得出<span class=\"name name-commodity\">具商業價值的數據</span>，也能找出<span class=\"name name-technology\">額外資源</span>。"
  },
